data.description: CHOLLA model Villa on PREMIUM  Cul-De-Sac LOT w/mountain views & no home or street behind! Kitchen features 42'' white cabinets with knobs, tile backsplash, granite counters, SS appliances, reverse osmosis, roll-out shelves, built-in trash bin, under cabinet & pendant lights. So many upgrades from the large tile flooring (carpet in the bedrooms only), Granite vanities, tile showers, water softener, Plantation shutters, tall baseboards, custom fans & lighting throughout. Garage has AC & Epoxy flooring. Step out back to the spacious covered patio w/pavers where you can relax & enjoy the beautiful Mountain views. Premium lot w/a wall & no homes behind. Lots of Privacy! The HOA takes care of the exterior of the villa, including the landscaping. Please come see this beautiful Villa today!!!
